message.entry: Only string and numeric arguments are accepted.
Inputs contain an "Inf" or "NaN", results may not be reliable.
Input matrices must be the same size.
A column-wise comparison is not possible with a row vector input.
A row-wise comparison is not possible with a column vector input.
Input row vector must contain as many elements as there are columns in the input matrix.
Input column vector must contain as many elements as there are rows in the input matrix.
